data.description: **Assumable for qualifying veterans at 2.65%** Discover this welcoming spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem. The large kitchen that opens to the dining space is perfect for gatherings. With a generously sized walk-out basement, it offers versatile space for various activities. Don't miss the fully fenced backyard. New furnace, AC, washer, dryer and more. Professionally painted interior is ready for you. Enjoy proximity to the lake, walking paths, parks, and excellent schools. Plus, convenient shopping is just a short drive away. Don't miss this opportunity!
